#advanced computer network
Design and implement a(socket programming) chat session application which enable multiple users chatting at the same time (threads) and design a user friendly interface for the chat program(Java Gui programming). 
The project apply a centralized structure. The server is the center for every client.
the server end create each client a thread to handle each client. so each thread is listening for the client. if the client send a message. Server get this message by according thread and broadcast the message to every client.
The client end create a thread for itself and the thread always watch for the user input. if the user input a word. the client should sent this message to the server by socket communication.